{"tid":1636040,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[請負皮] 其實我琴晚事前已講左唔好夜晚8點，明明放假點解非夜晚8點不可","createTime":"2019-10-07T16:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T11:12:30.000Z","uid":161430,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0e2057f2898b7376a16838cc93924b7055d7c4fd","tid":1636040,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:15:23.000Z","msg":"我亦已經講左，開花如果係第二次做，<br />\n今次狗會佈好防，我已經講左比你地知，<br />\n但當時只係有人負評。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6MDLbV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6MDLbV.png&h=b136cb60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QLiFYxj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQLiFYxj.png&h=71474b74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvJFYyp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvJFYyp.png&h=dab16679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有，一早講左星期5晚既狗，真係唔係刻意扮無警<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mtK9RWP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmtK9RWP.png&h=856bbacd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼續負皮我啦，但我其實每次都一定會知咩事，<br />\n但其他人唔聽，我真係冇辦法，我盡用身份提左架喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次大家小心啦，我嘔血喇，事前就負皮我，<br />\n見到難聽既真話，條氣又要唔順，結果事後又要後悔，又中曬伏。"},{"pid":"9103e8e95f0d13396562df9a2697ffa5a85e5995","tid":1636040,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:16:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">又話杯葛？<br />\n又話抗爭？<br />\n繼續俾錢佢賺去出賣港人？<br />\n和理非平時返工唔好再俾正價搭黨鐵！<br />\n無得揀嘅情況例外</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/237n0J0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F237n0J0.jpg&h=61248f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0TeRHg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0TeRHg.jpg&h=94f567e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFtRTVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFtRTVB.jpg&h=5322f0ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxJ20AB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxJ20AB.jpg&h=c7141e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFpQ9Cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFpQ9Cb.jpg&h=a7156522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果和理非連咁小野都做唔到<br />\n就唔好學人話抗爭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHxjrJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHxjrJf.jpg&h=8688cd40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">聽日<span style=\"color: red;\">全民三罷</span>！！！<br />\n當十幾歲嘅學生中槍，<br />\n咁多個人冇咗隻眼，<br />\n咁多個義士死諫，<br />\n仲可以正常返工返學？</span>"},{"pid":"5f99054d967fa5d8e8ea46a3f594fd35a17dd970","tid":1636040,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:16:39.000Z","msg":"I HAVE TOLD YOU"},{"pid":"fdd48e86cf6a618f86d92d2365ac380cb206a407","tid":1636040,"uid":161430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:18:34.000Z","msg":"跟住次次事後扮時運高 見唔倒有人曾經提過你咁<br />\n<br />\n我冇氣"},{"pid":"5fbb63c5c07994627268646d416a9ab3ee7effef","tid":1636040,"uid":243333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:19:31.000Z","msg":"女仔入 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1635795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1635795</a>"},{"pid":"15dbfbb5be44cae6f2f97fd22d1458920766f0a1","tid":1636040,"uid":25686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:20:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67440373988bdfcd157d4b0eaf3f9bca07f7186c","tid":1636040,"uid":191527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:22:04.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"f3f25ccc0046ade4c4cdda27605efec00175d39d","tid":1636040,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:26:04.000Z","msg":"請幫手推爆黑警散布謠言!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［極醜惡又一例證］香港警察又掩埋真相 鼓吹謠言散播<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1636039\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1636039</a>"},{"pid":"1077f52dfa9dc2f226e25c490d744bec193d01d5","tid":1636040,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:36:24.000Z","msg":"好多人都係接受唔到事實<br />\n<br />\n你地繼續活喺自己世界 又唔知自己蠢<br />\n次次都不知不覺比mon po狗同hk01引導左風向<br />\n<br />\n好似之前明明講好 假日係1pm會做18區<br />\n就算唔1pm, 都可以係下晝開始,<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但琴晚只要連登突然出張新文宣, 話夜晚8點<br />\n全世界就決定夜晚8點</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有有人吹風話等人權法, 你睇下, 果晚幾多人跟左<br />\n<br />\n仲有我講左根本冇空城計, 狗會照樣狂拉人, 結果今晚應驗<br />\n瀨野喇, 你地果堆蠢人就扮唔唔倒<br />\n<br />\n你地繼續啦, 我唔會再同d蠢人溝通咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登宜家被嚴重滲透, 我寧願花時間做文宣同上fb, twitter更好"},{"pid":"62ffe2c6f63331f843b938385126df7a9b573f6d","tid":1636040,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:37:15.000Z","msg":"成日都假期都唔知點解會定8點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df6c9893533cafa02d7907a1c510e95fc5d0a5b","tid":1636040,"uid":310858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u1Kt8Hm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu1Kt8Hm.jpg&h=bb17b96c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10461bb77c086ae01a5f476cd424889cbbd0a5bc","tid":1636040,"uid":282798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:40:40.000Z","msg":"其實快閃唔定時會好啲，幾多點都好，一早定咗嘅話，班狗都係有時間部署"},{"pid":"e60e4cd037b7663d83daa9ee9a553709cf58d02f","tid":1636040,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":